# bjf

Simple in-place JSON Formatter

## Install

### Install from pypi

```bash
pip3 install bjf
```

### Install from git
```bash
pip3 install "git+https://github.com/rohanwinsor/bjf.git"
```

## Usage
```
python -m bjf {source_file_or_directory}
```

